\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\div\grad u+\bar{s}=0\qc\vec{x}\in\Omega\label{eq:PoissonPDE}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

which is a 2nd order PDE
\begin_inset CommandInset nomenclature
LatexCommand nomenclature
symbol "PDE"
